{
  "text": "The \"hat\" terms in [CITATION_1] in the cell boundary terms from integration by parts are the so-called \"numerical fluxes\" [CITATION_2] , which are single valued functions defined on the edges and should be designed based on different guiding principles for different PDEs to ensure the stability. Here we take the simple choices such thatĥ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "122640139",
